Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.34,0:01:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分开了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒支配这座山的\N邪恶帝皇多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、火美子和武一郎师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.05,0:01:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边在各界层\N与多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边以第七界层为目标进发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上到第三界层的我们\N知道了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为极寒之剑和灼热之剑\N交换了的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.70,0:01:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令这里变成了灼热地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要令这里恢复原状\N便要找出极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得知了它在第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便一个人上到了第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.12,0:02:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当终于找出了极寒之剑时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼前出现了\N因为古拿玛出卖的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.13,0:02:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被捉的火美子和武一郎师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八话\N热啊热啊,飞走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇啊!摇啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.00,0:02:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎样做?小鬼\N如果你拔出那把极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们便会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.62,0:02:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道救世主会舍弃同伴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.51,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.46,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,不要理在下了\N喂!那里的呆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.64,0:03:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子?难道是叫我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你还有谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下怎样也无所谓\N但是请你放过火美子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,放我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.37,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N才不是会听这种话的人物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.03,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师、火美子\N放心吧,我来救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是来救我的吗?\N为…为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?\N我们不是同伴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴…同伴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同…同伴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请求你停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你说要求我吗?\N好,我停手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要你用手指\N插入鼻孔转三个圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再高呼所也所也大人万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想的话 ,不干也可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,我干便是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也大人万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子好古怪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干得高兴点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也大人万岁!\N太小声了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没出息了,渡!\N你这样也算是在下的徒弟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.09,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,够了,渡\N在下已经早有觉悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.68,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界,为了世人而死\N是武士的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,是身为男人的本份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这个身体烧掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂也会\N成为天空上灿烂的的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直地…一直地守护着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师…师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔兵,点火!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不想死\N不要!不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢,大叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要,还是不要\N在下还有很多东西想吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.57,0:06:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有山珍海味,鲍参翅肚\N我还是不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点点火吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧猪!烧猪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎办好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,我觉得很热我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…\N他来干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那部魔神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.96,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,击比伦部队\N不要给他们逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.67,0:07:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的子弹打不中的\N喂,你不反击吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说得轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会有事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题,一定可以顺利逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要快点拔出极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?\N要射准一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快,愉快\N差不多是时候走了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!要撞了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.45,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!可恶的古拿玛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也,去追击他们\N绝对不能让他们逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.04,0:08:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个上第四界层\N去收拾那个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么拔不出来啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话\N师傅和火美子会很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉,请你放手啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就算破坏胡娜拉像\N也要把剑取去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.97,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,走开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.94,0:09:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手,胡娜拉\N求求你帮助渡吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,请你把剑交给渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡取剑不是用来做坏事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.07,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了救自己的同伴\N和创界山的众生用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.97,0:09:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我求你\N请你把剑交给渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉像在哭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把剑放开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!\N终于把极寒之剑取到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉,谢谢你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是胡娜拉的眼泪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.82,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,你看\N这是极寒之剑啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次你干得很了不起\N但不可以只顾高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点回去第三界层不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢,我很担心大家\N走吧,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.97,0:10:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉像替我们开路了\N我们跳进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.66,0:10:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!雪,你和西蒙一起\N在千人仙人那处等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次我会把灼热之剑带回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.47,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心了,渡\N我一定会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!在下的背烧伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真烦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然救了他们\N我到底在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我已不能再变回原状了\N不只这样,连性命也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.34,0:11:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对了\N现在在这里解决了他们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨!在危险的时候\N让你救了我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽不知你是谁\N可以让我们见一见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!请等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到…要杀他们我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到哪里也没用\N你只有死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛…\N鸟先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是古拿玛驾驶那魔神的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该,我会替你作墓的你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在此之前要先收拾你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也,今次的对手是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你回来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!\N他逃过了残酷大人的追杀吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,把你们一起收拾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得到吗?\N龙神丸,用炎龙拳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么,反炎龙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的,龙神丸\N你的招式我们已全部研究过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.84,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!必杀性感热吻火炎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.13,0:13:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的高温火炎\N中了这招便完了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.16,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N对方是什么也能溶掉的高热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用什么也能冰封的寒气\N决胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸\N我把极寒之剑的力量传给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,试试吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.81,0:14:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的废剑有什么用?\N用这收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.66,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感热吻火炎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N就这样还给他吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极寒登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级屈辱啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.77,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,我一开始便是为了\N当间谍才成为你们的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此已没什么好说了\N随便你们处置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛是…多恶达的手下?\N你骗人吧?古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,在下还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在热岛被捉,是这家伙布局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部鸟形魔神\N便是最有力的证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饶恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,不要啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.28,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如你所愿\N把你的头砍下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.54,0:15:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确骗了你们\N来吧,因为我是间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.63,0:15:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,你好像已经觉悟了\N这样的话…我来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.39,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你们干什么?\N不要啊,快放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和火美子险些便被烧死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是古拿玛不是来救你了吗\N师傅,可以杀救命恩人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生是好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.51,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是这样,至今为止\N我们遇上了多少危险的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…\N那一定是有什么理由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴,渡,很多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能被你们唤做同伴已足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我已留下回忆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,快来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的一剑\N已把以前的古拿玛杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的泪水\N是从你的真心流出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活着便定会有好事发生\N好好生存吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!\N鸟先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,用极寒之剑吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉\N请你赐力量给极寒之剑吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个便是亚撒姆像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,你帮帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.26,0:17:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,让我骑上你的背吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚撒姆\N我是来把极寒之剑还给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把灼热之剑交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放回了,放回了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.76,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么放回了极寒之剑\N火炎也没有熄灭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底…\N啊!出路消失了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话\N我们会被烧死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?亚撒姆\N为什么火炎不熄灭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.50,0:18:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你为什么来这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把极寒之剑放回\N也不能令这世界复原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.11,0:19:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为多恶达\N把灼热之盾的龙之眼取走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之眼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.76,0:19:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有龙之眼\N也不能令这灼热地狱平息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.03,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,已来到这里\N竟也没有办法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要气妥,渡\N你冷静地想想,会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胡娜拉给我的胡娜拉之泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.12,0:20:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是胡娜拉和亚撒姆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.30,0:21:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹啊\N又一条彩虹恢复原状了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?老公公…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又去了哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂啊涂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…你再轻力一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.39,0:21:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是有古拿玛\N便不能令第三界层恢复原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生,我很喜欢你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们,混帐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!古拿玛你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何\N突然很想向着夕阳奔走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"伙伴"真是好东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!今次是第四界层了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.95,0:22:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!


